name: interferon induced protein with tetratricopeptide repeats 3
summary: Enables identical protein binding activity. Involved in negative regulation of apoptotic process; negative regulation of cell population proliferation; and response to virus. Located in cytosol and mitochondrion. [provided by Alliance of Genome Resources, Apr 2022]
